### SilloBite Connection Code API Tests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@email = test@example.com

### 1. Generate Connection Code (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/generate-code
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Verify Connection Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "code": "ABC123"
}

###

### 3. Test with Invalid Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "code": "INVALID"
}

###

### 4. Test with Missing Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "ABC123"
}

###

### 5. Test with Missing Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}"
}

###

### 6. Use Access Token (replace with actual token from step 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###
